  </Text>
  <Text type={'base'} class='mt-6 text-black w-[65%] max-md:w-[90%]'>
    We nurture active and empathetic lifelong learners with a global outlook. Our balanced academic approach is designed to foster personal development and crucial skills for today's world.
  </Text>
